response.original_title: Zombie Land Saga LIVE ~ Franchouchou, let's all join together!~ in SAGA
response.overview: Zombie Land Saga LIVE ~Franchouchou, let's all join together!~ in SAGA (ゾンビランドサガLIVE～フランシュシュみんなでおらぼう！～in SAGA, Zonbirandosaga raivu ~ furanshushu min'na de o-ra bō!~ In sāga) was a concert held on July 26, 2019, at the Furusato Kaikan Arpino Center, Saga, Japan. In which the idol group Franchouchou made a live performance before thousands of spectators, being one of the best presentations to date of the group.
